Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.91,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不過也會有一點點好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:49.25,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.33,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}世界很和平呢  去附近人家串門吧
