Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:01.17,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}看起來又有精氣神了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:01.47,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}是呢
