Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:16.53,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}未來的地圖在哪裡？既然不知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:18.49,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}還不如直接做出來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.16,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}「幸運點數」給我一大桶Please
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:29.62,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}心兒軟綿綿  感覺暖洋洋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:33.17,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想把這感覺分享給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:36.92,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}才不會無聊無聊無聊  一起來做各種各樣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.51,0:22:42.39,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}像兔子一樣飛跳起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.05,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}飛跳起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:48.06,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}連明天也要追趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:49.73,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一定要追趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:55.94,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}令人心跳的巧克力脆皮甜點♪  在嘴裡發出悅耳的清脆酥響
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:23:00.95,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悠悠哉哉  雖然輕鬆的話題根本說不完
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:04.99,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}閃閃發光地舞動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:06.62,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}舞動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.66,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fs18\pos(416,330)}Pirouette
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.66,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在樹蔭透過的日光下跳著迴旋舞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.21,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}轉來轉去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:18.13,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一瞬間握住你的手  讓腳步聲響徹街頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:25.93,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}可愛  美味  同一個時間  和你在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------TXT----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃  完全沉迷於芭蕾舞之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是自然而然就跳起芭蕾的程度了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打醉拳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天看到電視上播放的電影裡有醉拳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種藉口就像是麻耶一樣誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著花束的高中生有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天高中好像是畢業典禮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  我的志願到底怎麼選才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到了不得不去考慮它的時候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起畢業典禮  心愛她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還沒有畢業吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能不能升學啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你在擔心那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得學姐沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是說一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來不像是沒問題的樣子？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在畢業典禮的時候感動得不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇到我們了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且我一想到我自從來到這個小鎮已經快一年了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光陰似箭呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  看到了果然在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼哭起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們約好了要碰頭的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喝點茶慶祝升學什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們找到了家很棒的咖啡館呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃你們要不要一起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們出軌到其他的店了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要從兔子之家畢業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,座無虛席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和高中生組的座位分開來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想像她們那樣變成熟些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對後輩自然地說出「一起來喝茶吧」的邀請什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能自然地邀請別人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼惠  要不要試試看？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小姐你很可愛呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  一  一起來喝茶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是可疑的搭訕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗路學姐喝茶的姿勢好像大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種大人的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成為那樣的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:05:00.61,TXTH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs16}飲料（僅限無酒精飲料）  免費一杯券
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:05:00.61,TXTH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs16}只要用一張本券便可以兌換自選飲料一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這張券還可以使用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免費券是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無破綻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼有種妹妹會被人搶走的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有成熟一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點更優雅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是您的下午茶套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我並沒有點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是那邊的客人為您點的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡可不是酒吧啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們在高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是姐姐我為了可愛的妹妹們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親手獻上的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說  吃這個的時候是有著先後順序的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從三明治開始吃起吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是從司康餅開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞口水…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說如果不能優雅地吃掉這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就無法成為成熟的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡只要模仿紗路她們就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在吃熱狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊也點了一樣的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是模仿的好機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感受到有羨慕的視線呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可能正在被觀察著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觀察？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在確認我們是否為值得尊敬的學姐呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想通了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位！我所說的關於相對論的解釋清楚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在展示自己頭腦聰明！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比較狹義相對論和廣義相對論的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是更喜歡狹義點的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然接上話茬了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就算現在要背誦波若心經什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是小菜一碟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連紗路也？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}果然  廣義和狹義的比起來  概念有點太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狹義相對…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好像在享用之前需要先聊會天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要說些大人的話題呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前第一次拿哥哥跑腿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}買東西的話把JUMP買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可稱不上是大人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下  下次去酒吧時間的兔子之家坐坐看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好成熟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便徹夜長談怎麼樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐我可不會允許那種事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被聽到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是下午茶時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道怎麼吃這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的吃法不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的就好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山小姐所說的普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們的普通可不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  難道說我並不普通嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃她們正在和青山小姐聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是很重要的話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在向青山小姐咨詢意見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我已經觀察過她們了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不過她們可並不值得尊敬呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山小姐  下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被智乃她們拜託來觀察你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相…相對論嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狹義和廣義…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色…色即是空…空…空即是色…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我比較喜歡宇宙弦理論哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是稀奇啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  大家也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是巧合呢…我也…喜歡宇宙的弦理論…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不知道下午茶套餐的吃法所以在觀察我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模仿行動的時候不知不覺就跟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用把它想成什麼鄭重的東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  想要成為成熟的女性的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候只要開心地吃就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為禮儀本身就是能讓大家都開心而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教官的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深刻銘記於我心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  他們回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有空的位置  我們就把桌子拼起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來通過抽籤隨機排座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不能作弊把自己跟學妹們坐在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很公平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能夠和大家一起開茶會就已經很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也嘗一嘗這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  啊這個也嘗嘗看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因為離她們離得最遠就沮喪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我有想問的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都能問哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狹義相對論和廣義相對論有什麼區別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你們要顯擺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還得要再加把油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多問我先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那你打算怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作…作為姐姐要更加…好好有所成長才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃  我來替你拎包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用對姐姐客氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有對你客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那我來背你走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  咦  不要客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐寄來的信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的回信好快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛  已經早上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是春假  但是也不能睡懶覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身人偶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐要涼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎和平時不一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是早餐燒焦了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完早餐之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會好好教教你狹義相對論和廣義相對論的區別的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛的樣子很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起平時來說動作更敏捷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這  這是在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撫摸提比的動作也很敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎您光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招待客人的動作也很敏捷！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來帶您去座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是紳士呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(363.2,324)}牛郎店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被看作是另一種店的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劉海的方向和平時的完全相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軟綿綿  軟綿綿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軟綿綿的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本尊的話一定會忍不住抱上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認真工作的話是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼不過感覺很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到打擊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望心愛不要努力過度而發燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一語中的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做到這個份上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…會來哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說兩者有什麼關聯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓姐姐看到你努力的樣子對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得必須要振作點來著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為智乃的姐姐有在好好以身作則什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛的姐姐很嚴格嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  她很溫柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然上面還有兩個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她對他們說教的樣子好帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說教…調教師嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調教…我…我難道會比現在被管教得更嚴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}嗚嗚不要不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕到發抖了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:14:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以憧憬著姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來做妹妹的也有不少苦衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我來幫你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展現出你好的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過作為獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很羨慕你有那麼多兄弟姐妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理世…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會把理世作為我的妹妹來介紹的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…和智乃一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為普通的朋友就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐修行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣才能看起來很能幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想給姐姐看看我成長的一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先讓從剛才開始就一直怕得發抖的智乃鎮定下來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}調教師…會被摸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我在啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}別  別這樣  不要這樣嘛  好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是同樣的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這差距怎麼就這麼大呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果理世她們犯點迷糊什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來是不是就會顯得心愛很能幹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆向思維
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…既然我都已經說過要幫忙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我想下單…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我分不清楚咖啡的區別…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛  快來救場！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我數學很差的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心買進了一噸重的咖啡罐頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個天然呆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵包可以用火焰噴射器來烤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆這樣根本讓人看不下去嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可都是為了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就讓我們來鍛煉心愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託您了  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛  這裡可還留著灰塵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好像覺醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆模式…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把這個飛盤撿回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}看好了  要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是為了什麼的特訓啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.09,0:17:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你們…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.46,0:17:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想變得像姐姐那樣
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望你們來當我妹妹
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  人家想吃麵包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}來幫我寫作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…算…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這得持續到什麼時候為止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到心愛察覺到這並沒有什麼意義為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天謝謝大家幫我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一點拿鐵咖啡  不成敬意…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  是心愛畫的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起剛開始的時候  有很大進步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們一直都在看著所以沒有察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就是有在好好成長的證明嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直帥呆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那我現在就給你們畫個更厲害的東西好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看3D的拿鐵拉花！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算作為店員有所成長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作為姐姐來說還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3D拿鐵拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是提比吧喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛啊…真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管過多久都是不靠譜的姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是覺得心愛是一個好姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算嘴上說著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好展現出好的態度的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛只是因為姐姐要來就有點慌張過度了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不要太在意就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明最近心愛在的時候很開心來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗路  你在擔心心愛和智乃她們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得心愛應該對自己更有點自信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  紗路也應該對自己自信點才對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然把話題轉到我身上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為人家有點擔心紗路嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要擔心人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時隔一年的重逢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是讓人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅有期待  也有不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個心愛很罕見地在煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為姐姐的成長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是個不知天高地厚的煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然同為一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情可不是勉強自己而是好好傳達才行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偶爾也會說出些有道理的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也有個不知天高地厚的兒子在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她差不多應該到車站了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去接她真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信裡好像寫著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我自己會來店裡的  想看看心愛工作時的樣子」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的吧？  心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…咦咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛因為過於緊張而藍屏了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快去接客啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信裡不是寫著要你好好工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂  心愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛的…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她會是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:40.57,TXTI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frx12\fry8\pos(322.4,107.6)\frz317.3}變成兔子的咖啡師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是不妙的狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具體來說是怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…估計會變得很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.09,0:23:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是指不妙的部分
